## ✊🏾 **Major Struggles & Contributions of African Americans**

### **1️⃣ Slavery, Emancipation & Reconstruction (1619–1877)**

- **Chattel slavery** defined the early African American experience in the U.S.
- Resistance through **rebellions (Nat Turner, Denmark Vesey) and abolitionism**.
- **Reconstruction (1865–1877)** briefly expanded Black rights before Jim Crow laws rolled back progress.

