## ⚖️ **Challenges & Future of African American Liberation**

⚠️ **Systemic Racism** – Disparities in wealth, education, health, and incarceration persist.  
⚠️ **Voter Suppression & Political Representation** – New forms of disenfranchisement.  
⚠️ **Gentrification & Urban Displacement** – Economic forces threaten Black communities.  
⚠️ **Technology & AI Bias** – Digital discrimination disproportionately affects Black people.

🔗 **Possible Solutions:**

- **Reparations & Economic Justice** 💰
- **Education & Policy Reform** 📚
- **Digital Activism & AI for Racial Justice** 🤖

